===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|linguistics|translation studies}} The act or product of [[transliterating]], of representing [[letter]]s or [[word]]s in the [[character]]s of another [[alphabet]] or [[script]].
# {{lb|en|sign language}} The act or product of rendering [[speech]] in [[sign language]], or vice versa.

